Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登富士山的日子终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从新宿出发 大约两个半小时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午十点过后 我们到达了富士五合目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.29,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(560,430)}初次见面 富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好凉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为五合目已经是标高2300米左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该比下面低10度以上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山的高度好像是3776米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一半的话 是1888米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五合目不是一半的高度对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 几合目和高度距离好像没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一种说法是按照登山的难度为标准决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说 从五合目到六合目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从六合目到七合目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有从七合目到八合目 虽然距离很短
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路却越来越艰险 一样的疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越往上越艰险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加…加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是邮局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有兑换所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里为止自行车也可以通行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到七合目为止 可以骑马哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过用自己的双腿登上去 一定会更加感动的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就一边让身体适应 一边吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山因为标高很高 容易得高山病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山病？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在标高很高的地方勉强登山的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会头疼 变得很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分的情况 到山脚下一下就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可不要勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 爆炸咖喱 很有趣啊 我吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃野菜荞面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云海拉面？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是什么样的拉面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说成是云海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馄饨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡蛋汤？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是山药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱 我要吃云海拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待云海拉面是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是爆炸咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米饭是富士山 福神渍是熔岩啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云海拉面是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是普通的拉面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是普通的拉面 但是很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 吃得好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土特产有各种各样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 买一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来再买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 会成为负担的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(522,617)\frz3.4}可以成为纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(95,56)}附加铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(148,111)}附加铃铛 旗帜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(148,168)}附加铃铛 帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金刚杖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以在登顶途中的山间小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把烙印印在这只杖上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把烙印都集齐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把烙印都集齐的话 会成为很好的纪念哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz355.236\pos(642,294)}希望可以平安登顶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz352.801\pos(841,434)}葵    枫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz352.97\pos(818,591)}日向   心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 现在开始登山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再打给你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就向富士山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 麦克 等等我 再慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还很轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是最后也是这样 就轻松了…不可能这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山分为须走路线 御殿场路线等几个登山路线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们登的是最普通的吉田路线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从五合目开始 经过六合目 七合目 八合目到达本八合目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里留宿山间小屋 好好休养再上山顶出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为山间小屋有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算一边进行适当的休息一边登山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是六合目了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才只走了30分钟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急 山是不会逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前路很长呢 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃点心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就要吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 在肚子饿之前吃是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是从枫那现学现卖的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面筋？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟老爷爷似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 膨胀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为气压差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来正要向着七合目出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难受的话 哪怕在路上也要返回哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可以勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太担心了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再给你打电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在走一样的路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是岩石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推土机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那个往山间小屋运送食物和水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能让我们坐上去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七合目到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第二个了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山间小屋真的有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉十步就有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑雪杖的顶端掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 大家一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根滑雪杖还挺贵的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么容易就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷不冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难受的话不要顾虑尽管说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我只是晃了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真的是登山道？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是山崖一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根杖变得碍事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 不过大家都会觉得富士山很容易登
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 这是第八个了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到葵了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 谢谢
